title: Supercars Exposed-Speed Channel-Spyker-Mulholland.F430.997T.Exig
description: SuperCars Exposed, Speed Channel (US) 2008, Hosted by Tanner Foust, 22 mins.  Tanner drives Spyker C8 Spyder.  Plus a timed competition between Tanner and Townsend Bell on hilly section of Mulholland Drive behind the wheels of Ferrari F430, Porsche 997 Turbo, and Sector 111 Lotus Exige.  MP4 file, H264 codec, 640x480, captured from digital SDTV.  More episodes to come from tallearthling.
